This script listens for the WordpressUlikeUpdated event fired by WP ULike whenever a user interacts with a like/unlike button. It extracts relevant details such as action type, content ID, content type, and updated counter, then pushes this data to the GTM Data Layer. This allows you to track engagement events in Google Tag Manager and send them to Google Analytics 4 for analysis.
